comment: Refreshing and a hint of crisp citrusy after taste. Definitely worth a try.
Wow - one of the smoothest whiskey sat this age (2yrs) that I've tasted. Not much of a long finish, but excellent flavors on the into total sip and very drinkable.

I was surprised by this... deep flavor, I got a lot of spice and caramel.  Would definitely get another bottle if I could find it.

Was a gift from a Neb friend.  Going to ask him for another one.
Spicy rye blends into green apple and salty caramel
